# sources/wget-list — effective download URL list for ft_linux (systemd variant)
# =============================================================================
# DERIVED FROM env/versions.sh. This is a flat, human-readable copy of every
# *_URL declared there, for quick reference and for `wget -i sources/wget-list`.
# The AUTHORITATIVE source is env/versions.sh; sources/download-sources.sh reads
# the URLs straight from it, so if a version changes there, regenerate this file:
#
#     bash -c 'source env/versions.sh
#       for n in $(compgen -v | grep -E "_URL$" | sort); do printf "%s\n" "${!n}"; done' \
#       > sources/wget-list   # (then re-add this header)
#
# Lines starting with '#' are comments and are ignored by `wget -i`.
# This is the SYSTEMD-variant list (systemd/dbus/meson/ninja/openssl/elfutils/
# libffi/zstd are included; Eudev/Sysvinit/Sysklogd/Udev-lfs are NOT — see
# sources/wget-list-sysv and docs/03-systemd-deviation.md).
# =============================================================================
